section.def:
Commission
                (委員會) means Minimum Wage Commission established
            by section 11;

Commissioner
                (處長) has the same meaning as in the Employment
            Ordinance (Cap. 57);

employer
                (僱主) has the same meaning as in the Employment
            Ordinance (Cap. 57);

hours
                worked
                (工作時數)—see section 4;

wage
                period
                (工資期)—see section 5;

wages
                (工資), subject to section 6, has the
            same meaning as in the Employment Ordinance (Cap. 57);
